headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Amphenol After Its 101% Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Amphenol is still a smart buy after its huge run, or if you might be late to the party, this breakdown is designed to help you make a clear, value focused assessment. The stock has climbed about 1.7% over the last week and 0.3% over the past month, but the real eye opener is its roughly 101% gain over the last year and more than 265% over three years. This naturally raises questions about how much upside is left versus the risk now reflected in the price. Behind...
